01:10:32,461 --> 01:10:34,622
Oh, baseball.

1116
01:10:34,663 --> 01:10:36,460
Jako uzbudljiv sport.

1117
01:10:38,133 --> 01:10:40,397
Mislim da bih radije gledala 
travu kako raste.

1118
01:10:42,571 --> 01:10:44,129
Hvala.

1119
01:10:48,177 --> 01:10:50,270
Hej.

1120
01:10:52,081 --> 01:10:53,810
Dobro, decki, evo za vas.

1121
01:10:53,849 --> 01:10:55,874
Hej. Dobila je infekciju.
Morali su je odvesti.

1122
01:10:55,918 --> 01:10:58,318
- Molim?
- Odveli su Katherine na operaciju.

1123
01:11:15,838 --> 01:11:17,669
- Tamo su prijeko, gospodine.
- Oh.

1124
01:11:17,706 --> 01:11:19,435
- Hvala.
- Molim.

1125
01:11:19,475 --> 01:11:21,909
- Hej, Amone.
- Hej.

1126
01:11:21,944 --> 01:11:24,936
- Kyle, kako si, kompa?
- Dobro.

1127
01:11:24,980 --> 01:11:27,346
- Kako si ti, Virg'?
- Kyle.

1128
01:11:27,383 --> 01:11:32,685
Upravo sam razgovarao
sa šefom odjela.

1129
01:11:32,721 --> 01:11:35,781
Kaže mi da je kirurg kojeg 
su doveli za nju...

1130
01:11:35,824 --> 01:11:38,054
...jedan od najboljih u zemlji.

1131
01:11:38,093 --> 01:11:40,493
Vele da je jako cijenjen.

1132
01:11:40,529 --> 01:11:42,622
Da.

1133
01:11:42,665 --> 01:11:45,259
Dakle...

1134
01:11:46,302 --> 01:11:48,702
...bit ce sve u redu s njom.

1135
01:12:06,021 --> 01:12:09,013
Hej, kako je ona?

1136
01:12:09,058 --> 01:12:13,017
Još uvijek je u operacijskoj 
dvorani.

1137
01:12:13,062 --> 01:12:15,462
Doktori nam ništa ne govore.

1138
01:12:16,699 --> 01:12:21,261
Ali mislim da traje duže
nego što smo ocekivali.

1139
01:12:21,303 --> 01:12:23,669
Dakle...

1140
01:12:24,973 --> 01:12:27,999
- Hej, gledaj...
-Nisam... nisam ljuta na tebe.

1141
01:12:30,045 --> 01:12:31,603
Razumijem.

1142
01:12:37,519 --> 01:12:39,714
Pa, još uvijek cekamo, stoga...

1143
01:12:42,925 --> 01:12:44,552
Zdravo, ljudi.

1144
01:12:46,995 --> 01:12:51,125
Dobro, dakle, zadržat cemo je 
ovdje još oko 10 dana...

1145
01:12:51,166 --> 01:12:55,102
...da vidimo kako napreduje,
ali mislim da ce biti dobro.

1146
01:12:55,137 --> 01:12:57,264
Oh.

1147
01:12:58,574 --> 01:13:01,065
Ali, istina je da nikad 
više nece biti ista.

1148
01:13:02,911 --> 01:13:05,436
Reci cu da ako bude pazila
na sebe...

1149
01:13:05,481 --> 01:13:07,278
...ako zakrpa ne popusti...

1150
01:13:07,316 --> 01:13:10,012
...onda mislim da ima 
jako dobre šanse.

1151
01:13:10,052 --> 01:13:12,043
No, hvala vam, doktore.

1152
01:13:12,087 --> 01:13:13,850
Hvala vam što ste spasili
moju djevojcicu.

1153
01:13:13,889 --> 01:13:15,254
Da, gospodine.

1154
01:13:15,290 --> 01:13:16,780
Prebacit ce je na intenzivnu...

1155
01:13:16,825 --> 01:13:19,020
...pa ce vam onda sestra 
pokazati gdje je...

1156
01:13:19,061 --> 01:13:22,326
...tako da je možete vidjeti.
- Zahvalni smo vam, doktore.

1157
01:13:22,364 --> 01:13:24,525
- Jesmo li se vec ranije sreli?
- Ne.

1158
01:13:24,566 --> 01:13:26,591
Ali mi je zaista drago što
sam vas sad upoznao.

1159
01:13:26,635 --> 01:13:29,035
Dobro.

1160
01:13:59,034 --> 01:14:00,865
Izvoli.

1161
01:14:04,106 --> 01:14:05,869
- Hvala.
- Mm-hmm.

1162
01:14:37,272 --> 01:14:39,797
Sanjala sam.

1163
01:14:41,543 --> 01:14:43,511
Da?

1164
01:14:44,947 --> 01:14:46,539
O cemu?

1165
01:14:51,787 --> 01:14:53,379
Ne znam.

1166
01:14:55,591 --> 01:14:57,752
Oboje smo bili u snu.

1167
01:14:57,793 --> 01:14:59,818
Toga se sjecam.

1168
01:14:59,862 --> 01:15:01,727
I to je bilo lijepo.

1169
01:15:03,699 --> 01:15:06,065
No, pa znaš kako to ide.

1170
01:15:07,069 --> 01:15:09,128
Ustat ceš, popit ceš svoju kavu...

1171
01:15:09,171 --> 01:15:12,140
...a onda, kako dan bude odmicao,...

1172
01:15:12,174 --> 01:15:14,233
...pocet ceš otkrivati
malene tragove.

1173
01:15:16,879 --> 01:15:18,744
Da.

1174
01:15:21,149 --> 01:15:22,741
Volim kako to ide.

1175
01:15:22,784 --> 01:15:24,217
Maleni tragovi.

1176
01:15:34,062 --> 01:15:37,190
Život je bio tako nov
i uzbudljiv.

1177
01:15:37,232 --> 01:15:39,257
Da, bio je.

1178
01:16:04,626 --> 01:16:06,355
Razgovarao sam s doktorima.

1179
01:16:06,395 --> 01:16:09,330
Vele da ceš biti dobro.

1180
01:16:20,709 --> 01:16:22,768
Kako nam je sin?

1181
01:16:27,149 --> 01:16:29,549
Našeg sina je odgojila
izuzetna žena.

1182
01:16:29,585 --> 01:16:31,678
Mislim da ce i on
biti dobro.

1183
01:16:42,230 --> 01:16:45,199
Nakon što se vec 82 godine
motam uokolo...

1184
01:16:45,233 --> 01:16:46,962
...jednu sam stvar skužio...

1185
01:16:47,002 --> 01:16:49,436
... jedno zasigurno znam.

1186
01:16:51,173 --> 01:16:52,970
Da? A što to?

1187
01:16:54,910 --> 01:16:57,174
Ne mogu ti reci.

1188
01:16:57,212 --> 01:16:58,975
Što?

1189
01:16:59,014 --> 01:17:01,539
Htio bih, zaista....

1190
01:17:01,583 --> 01:17:04,074
... ali sad to ne mogu izraziti
rijecima.

1191
01:17:06,088 --> 01:17:09,251
Ima li neki razlog...

1192
01:17:09,291 --> 01:17:11,020
...zašto si to uopce
spomenuo?

1193
01:17:13,295 --> 01:17:15,422
Došlo mi je da pricam.

1194
01:17:19,868 --> 01:17:20,664
Ahh.

1195
01:17:28,810 --> 01:17:30,710
- Hej.
- Hej.

1196
01:17:37,719 --> 01:17:39,584
Carltone, nešto ti moram reci.

1197
01:17:39,621 --> 01:17:41,213
Necu više igrati baseball.

1198
01:17:41,256 --> 01:17:44,248
O cemu to pricaš?

1199
01:17:44,292 --> 01:17:46,886
Mislim da mi se zapravo
nikada nije zaista sviðao.

1200
01:17:46,928 --> 01:17:48,987
- To ti je bio citav život.
-Znam.

1201
01:17:50,365 --> 01:17:52,356
Ali ne želim da mi bude.

1202
01:17:54,436 --> 01:17:55,562
Ne više.

1203
01:17:55,604 --> 01:17:58,471
Što ceš raditi?

1204
01:18:00,108 --> 01:18:03,009
Natjerati "The Gazette" da me
 uzmu da pišem o sportu.

1205
01:18:04,012 --> 01:18:06,913
Mogao bih možda raditi
na svojoj knjizi.

1206
01:18:06,948 --> 01:18:08,973
Znaci, bit ceš pisac.

1207
01:18:09,017 --> 01:18:10,814
Ah, možda.

1208
01:18:18,994 --> 01:18:22,327
Carltone, nije mi on zarucnik.

1209
01:18:24,800 --> 01:18:26,825
Ne znam zašto sam ga
uopce tako nazvala.

1210
01:18:38,580 --> 01:18:40,013
Gledaj.

1211
01:18:41,683 --> 01:18:44,811
Znam da cu s vremena na vrijeme
zeznuti stvari...

1212
01:18:44,853 --> 01:18:50,223
...i znam da stvari nece
biti savršene...

1213
01:18:53,562 --> 01:18:56,621
...ali ako mi pružiš još 
jednu priliku...

1214
01:18:58,166 --> 01:19:01,500
...kunem se Bogom da te više
nikad necu povrijediti.

1215
